FBIS3-49747 "dreeu010_b_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-010 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Jan 1994 BULGARIA Defense Ministry Denies Differences With Zhelev AU1301181494 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1700 GMT 13 Jan 94 AU1301181494 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Language: Bulgarian Article Type:BFN [Text] There are no differences regarding military policy between the leaderships of the Defense Ministry and the Armed Forces and the President of the Republic, Dr. Zhelev. This is the official stance of the Defense Ministry, which was announced at the Ministry's regular news conference held in Sofia today, in connection with certain reports in the press regarding the president's decree on setting up a military office. Tsvyatko Donchev, chief of the Defense Ministry Press Service, once again confirmed Defense Minister Aleksandrov's categorical refusal to comment on the letter published in the 24 CHASA daily.
